snippet.title: Banquet for Fools Gameplay First Look
snippet.description:
Banquet for Fools is a party-based action adventure RPG coming out next year, and is in Early Access until then. There is a demo and page here with more info:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/3172700/Banquet_for_Fools/?beta=1

Here's a website with some other stuff!
https://banquetforfools.com/

Thanks for checking it out!
Hannah & Joseph
